infinit-cli - Command line tool for Infinit.

Launching Infinit successfully can be done in a few steps:
 * Register a new account and start the Infinit shell.
    local-user$ ./infinit-cli register shell

 * Start Infinit instances (in the Infinit shell)
    infinit-user$ start

Next, you can:
 * Create a new network:
    infinit-user$ create_network MyNetwork

 * Invite a friend to a network:
    infinit-user$ invite my@friend.com MyNetwork

 * You might need to refresh networks with
    infinit-user$ refresh_networks

